<p>I got my bow, not the way I had planed, but I have it now none the less.   I tried to get past the storm giants that see through cammo and they killed me.  Fortunately, I died near the banner, behind Gleed.  I am very KOS to all giants.  I found a cleric with good faction to give me a res where my corpse was.  Cleric (Soulus) did not get aggroed since no giants were near.  I used sneak and became indifferent to Gleed.  The funny thing is I was KOS to the wolf near Gleed at the same time.  This is because I was in front of the wolf and behind Gleed.  I turned run off and went towards the banner slowly.  You have to get very close to the edge to make the trade.  You can see Gleed’s back very clearly when you are this close and look down.  I made sure he still coned indifferent and made the trade.  I then made a dash for the zone and was killed very quickly, but not until I made is past where the storm giants stand.  It was then easy to cammo, retrieve my corpse and get another res.<br />
