<i>Posted by Borzak on 11-21-2001 05:32 PM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>Since everyone links to this walkthru and it gets asked everytime does it still work. Here is my experience, second week of november 2001.<br />
<br />
Killed the named wum in GD twice, me (51) and 55 ranger. Took forever but doable, to get the whip.<br />
<br />
Made lvl 1 ogres that worship rallos zek and took them to Kael to look around un-KOS to get the layout for the upcoming sneak.<br />
<br />
Hung around kael a day or two until a guild was going that way to gleed. Asked if when they cleared to Gleed I could do the quest, they said yup.<br />
<br />
They cleared the 3 see invis giants, first my friend snuck up on him and got the bow - then me. Then we killed him and I got the flamesong.<br />
<br />
People ask why do the quest when you can just kill him. It's possible to do the quest first for whoever has the tail then kill him and get the bow some more.<br />
<br />
You don't have to jump down behind gleed it is possible to trade to him from up on the ledge if your careful and get right beside the flag pole, use 3rd person if you have to.<br />
<br />
Have fun.<FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2"><br>
